import React from 'react'
import {Navbar, Container} from 'react-bootstrap'
function NavbarComp() {
    return (
        <>
          <Navbar expand="lg" variant="light" bg="light">
            <Container>
                <Navbar.Brand href="#">Navbar</Navbar.Brand>
            </Container>
            </Navbar>  
        </>
    )
}

export default NavbarComp
